Source   Edit  

Gitea API client for Nim

This library provides a comprehensive client for interacting with Gitea's REST API. It supports repositories, issues, pull requests, users, organizations, and more.

proc newGiteaClient(baseUrl: string; token: string = ""): GiteaClient {.
    ...raises: [ResourceExhaustedError], tags: [ReadEnvEffect], forbids: [].}

Create a new Gitea API client Will use the provided token, or look for the GITEA_TOKEN environment variable.

Args: baseUrl: The base URL of your Gitea instance (e.g., "https://gitea.example.com") token: Optional API token for authentication
